# Regenerable live renders (run: vitest --config tools/design-parity/vitest.config.mjs)
surfaces/*/live/

# Regenerable measurement artifacts. `extract-computed.js` emits the design-*/
# live-* computed-style dumps and `compare.mjs` emits a JSON mirror of each
# report — all reproducible from the committed design harness + anchors, and
# noisy in review (tens of thousands of lines of getComputedStyle output).
#
# Deliberately still COMMITTED, because they are the durable record and are not
# reproducible from the tree alone:
#   surfaces/*/anchors.json        hand-authored design↔live selector map
#   surfaces/*/out/findings.json   the ranked punch-list
#   surfaces/*/out/*.md            the human-readable reports + FINDINGS
surfaces/*/out/design-*.json
surfaces/*/out/live-*.json
surfaces/*/out/report*.json
